    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car has been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s still looking and driving like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one\u2014always garaged and kept spotless. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
