    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have got to see this absolute gem! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in truly incredible, flawless shape\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. I am genuinely sad to see it go, but I\u2019m looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. It drives like a total dream and still has that wonderful fresh feel inside. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
