    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained for the discerning purist. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS system, providing a linear power band and a 7,900 RPM redline. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach: the critical rod bearing service has been performed using treated shells, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Finished in its original factory paint with zero signs of oxidation, the chassis remains stiff and responsive, retaining its original suspension geometry. All bushings, cooling system components, and seals are in peak operational condition, making this a true turn-key collector's piece.",
